text: Vineland is a city in Cumberland County, New Jersey, United States. As of the 2020 United States Census, the city had a total population of 60,780. Vineland, Millville and Bridgeton are the three main New Jersey cities of the Vineland–Millville–Bridgeton metropolitan statistical area.DP-1 - Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics: 2010 for Vineland-Millville- Bridgeton, NJ Metro Area , United States Census Bureau.
